sub_title: advisor and retired lector / professor Sustainable Business Operation at Avans Hogeschool / University Applied Sciences
summary:
research, training and advising on strategic and profitable business models for making a business really sustainanable. introducing Sustainable Business 3.0: the strategic approach.

Projects, research and publications on sustainable education, sustainable chemical engineering, biobased economy and circulair economy.
In particular with attention for practical implementation and the options and requirements of small and medium sized enterprises.

Papers are published and accessible on:
  https://www.academia.edu/
  https://www.researchgate.net/ 
  https://www.hbo-kennisbank.nl
